  <summary>A service wrapper to hoptoadapp.com.</summary>
  <description>hoptoadapp.com is a service to collect all kinds of &amp;quot;errors&amp;quot; from your applications.

Services_Hoptoad is a wrapper around hoptoadapp.com's API (Version 2). Currently this service wrapper supports web and also cli apps.

To communicate with hoptoadapp.com's API, we require either cURL, HTTP_Request2 or Zend_Http_Client.
</description>
